text: Esky is a trademarked brand of portable cooler from Australia Esky or Eskies may also refer to: * a nickname for the Edmonton Eskimos of the Canadian Football League * a nickname for the city of Escanaba, Michigan ** also a nickname of the city's high school, Escanaba Senior High School * a nickname or mascot of Esquire * "The Esky", a nickname of Nick Malceski (born 1984), former Australian rules footballer * Esky, a character in the 1980s animated TV series Snorks
title: Esky (disambiguation)
